_frontpage_headline_shop_EN.gif',NULL,'2026-02-11 19:02:02','2026-02-11 19:02:02',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('b546a6f9-2ec4-42be-a74a-b3e3000e5562',1,'furniture','default','Wired Effects','Effects are what happens after you activate a Trigger. To program an Effect, place it in your room, double click on it and set it up! You will always need to stack a Trigger with the Effect to make it work.','icon_82.png','wiredeffects_header.gif','wiredeffects_teaser.gif','2026-02-26 20:05:52','2026-02-26 20:06:33','8d10ae95-5500-462d-abc1-96b8b53338db',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('b90f61f3-0f29-49f9-a6ed-a7c93abfad20',0,'pets','pets','Horses','You can ride your horse around the Hotel and also customize your horses\' body and hair color.','icon_132.png','catalog_header_horse.png','','2026-03-12 16:22:15','2026-03-12 16:22:15','7134f854-20a6-4daf-aaf6-658cb468513f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('bd27cc4f-f3b5-448d-af23-2aec6d338621',0,'furniture','default','Wired Triggers','Triggers let you define what needs to happen for an Effect to take place. To program a Trigger, place it in a room, double click on it and set it up! You need to stack an Effect with the Trigger to make it work.','icon_81.png','wiredtriggers_header.gif','wiredtriggers_teaser.gif','2026-02-26 20:03:24','2026-02-26 20:03:24','8d10ae95-5500-462d-abc1-96b8b53338db',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('bf557a12-5ec1-4558-bf8b-6db277b6d37b',0,'furniture','default','Valentine 2015','','','','','2026-03-26 18:56:18','2026-03-26 18:56:18','e96efa12-80ad-466d-8506-ca52097cf300',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c0b380e3-4ccf-4b31-b521-61ef6ca26d92',0,'furniture','default','Cowboy','','','','','2026-03-28 21:17:46','2026-03-28 21:17:46','30e041a1-9d01-488c-9efd-892f78aa573e',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c1d3e237-7442-4e5c-9c13-7862a565fb76',0,'furniture','default','Teleporters','Habbo Doors are actually space-age teleport boxes that beam you from one room to another! Buy a pair, put one in each room and you\'ve got your own suite! You can either link two of your own rooms or link to a friend\'s (just give them one of the doors). From only 3 Credits a pair.','icon_58.png','doors_header.gif','teleports_teaser2.gif','2026-02-16 19:05:00','2026-02-16 19:05:00','acf1bac8-250a-4c01-8681-9bd4aa43435f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c1fc3bfe-0d14-40c6-a691-506194f509a9',0,'furniture','default','Area','Clean, chunky lines set this collection apart as a preserve of the down-to-earth Habbo. It\'s beautiful in this simplicity, and welcoming to every Habbo. Male, female, old, young, straight, gay: all will feel at home with the uncluttered, though highly funtional and comfortable, Area Collection','icon_14.png','area_header.gif','area_teaser.gif','2026-02-16 19:12:57','2026-02-28 11:28:10','acf1bac8-250a-4c01-8681-9bd4aa43435f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c3dfb2fd-56ab-4d8e-a5fc-59b1b516f618',0,'furniture','default','Accessories','However you place your essential furniture, it\'s the finishing touch that counts!','icon_11.png','accessories_header.gif','accessories_teaser.gif','2026-02-11 19:02:03','2026-02-28 11:30:52','acf1bac8-250a-4c01-8681-9bd4aa43435f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c40a7d92-2a9b-4f69-903c-803d2f9fd6de',0,'furniture','default','Dimmers','Check out the Mood Lights. Use these items to dim the light in your rooms. Try out different light settings with different wallpapers to see what you get. Talk about lighting with style!','icon_51.png','dimmers_header.gif','dimmers_teaser.gif','2026-02-11 19:02:03','2026-02-28 11:31:00','acf1bac8-250a-4c01-8681-9bd4aa43435f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('c5b6399c-5086-4c20-bfc2-8cb864387725',0,'furniture','default','Lost Tribe','','icon_38.png','LT_header_en.gif','catalog_tribal_teaser1_nl.gif','2026-03-15 15:30:51','2026-03-15 15:31:15','eb04e703-7486-4904-84d2-dfb8098617a0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('cddc482c-f8ed-4a5b-8162-c848ae2d5c89',0,'pets','pets','Terriers','The Cairn Terrier is one of the oldest terrier breeds, from the Scottish Highlands it was used f